reviewText: The teacher teaches too many things but they all are too superficial.
Video lessons many times lack context, explanation and do not seem align with objectives or presented in a way that doesn't make the connection clear. This course needs deeper explanations or a text.
G​ood course, but covering all 3 major cloud platforms at the same time is sometimes a little bit confusing. Also the quizzes are far too simple since many wrong answers are too obvious.

I​ would say this is a great course covering the main theme of "Cloud Virtualization, Containers and APIs". Sometimes it wasn't enough details, but totally there was a lot of new information for me. The instructor gives a lot of information that is useful to select for the next deep learning due to the own directions. 
There were several issues in the course, that need to be updated. The last task is tough and requires deep knowledge, but is optional.
Fantastic! Thank you.This course was an eye-opener for me.
